data.description: BEAUTIFUL POOL HOME W/OPEN FLOOR PLAN, BUILT 2021, ON OVERSIZED LOT!! Summerville II model, one story, featuring 3 bedrooms + den, 3 bathrooms and 3 car garage. This is the most popular + sought-after floorplan in Portico! Modern Smart Home, 2,445 sq.ft under A/C, perfect for family living and entertaining. Great Room w/high ceilings. Tall glass sliding doors. Gourmet Kitchen, huge granite island w/bar, stainless appliances & walk in pantry. Spacious Owner Suite w/private lanai access, two walk-in closets and en-suite bathroom w/large walk-in shower. Extra Den w/French Doors is ideal for a home office or hobby space. Many upgrades throughout. Covered lanai and swimming pool w/screen enclosure. Enjoy beautiful lake views from the pool deck + cozy outdoor relaxing. NO DAMAGE FROM HURRICANE IAN. NO FLOOD INSURANCE REQUIRED!  Portico is a highly sought-after community w/Low HOA fees. Amenities include clubhouse, community pool, gym, yoga/exercise room, tennis, pickleball, basketball, play area. Pets, Fences & LSVs permitted! Great location, short drive to I-75, shopping, dining & more!
